snippet: Two popular Russian rock musicians, disillusioned with the presidency of Dmitri A. Medvedev, have said they will not play next March’s presidential election as they did nearly four years ago.
lead_paragraph: Two popular Russian rock musicians, disillusioned with the presidency of Dmitri A. Medvedev, have said they will not play next March’s presidential election as they did nearly four years ago.

headline.main: Rock Stars Won’t Play for Putin
